    this ⟼ exp(- B θ / 2) = cos(|B| θ / 2) - B sin(|B| θ / 2) / |B|

    Parameters

    • B: BivectorE3

      The (unit) bivector generating the rotation.

    • θ: number

      The rotation angle in radians when the rotor is applied on both sides as R M ~R

    Returns this
